#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global Themes"
msgstr "Globalne teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Global Themes provide a common look and feel for many components at once:"
msgstr ""
"Globalne teme zagotavljajo skupen videz in občutek za več komponent hkrati:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Desktop Layout: An arrangement of panels and widgets - for example a bottom "
"panel with a task manager and application launcher, or a top panel with "
"global menu and system tray"
msgstr ""
"Postavitev namizja: Razporeditev plošč in gradnikov - na primer spodnja "
"plošča z upraviljalnikom opravil in zaganjalnikom aplikacij ali zgornja "
"plošča z globalnim menijem in sistemsko vrstico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Scheme: Color palette used throughout &plasma; and applications"
msgstr "Barvna shema: Barvna paleta, uporabljena povsod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Application Style: Appearance of user interface elements such as buttons, "
"menus, and scroll bars"
msgstr ""
"Slog aplikacije: Videz elementov uporabniškega vmesnika, kot so gumbi, "
"meniji in drsni trakovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma Style: Appearance of panels and widgets"
msgstr "Slog plazme: Videz plošč in gradnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Decoration: Window borders and titlebar buttons"
msgstr "Dekoracija oken: obrobe oken in gumbi naslovne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icons: Icons used throughout &plasma; and applications"
msgstr "Ikone: Ikone, ki se uporabljajo povsod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cursors: Mouse pointers"
msgstr "Kazalke: Kazalci miške"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Task Switcher: Overlay for switching between open windows, typically invoked "
"with the keyboard shortcut Alt+Tab"
msgstr ""
"Preklopnik opravil: prekrivni element za preklapljanje med odprtimi okni, "
"običajno priklican z bližnjico na tipkovnici Alt+Tab"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Splash Screen: Loading screen shown during &plasma; startup"
msgstr "Zaslon dobrodošlice: zaslon za nalaganje, prikazan med &plasma; začeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Login Screen: Screen with a user selector and password prompt shown when the "
"computer is started up"
msgstr ""
"Zaslon za prijavo: zaslon z izbirnikom uporabnika in pozivom za geslo, "
"prikazan ob zagonu računalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lock Screen: Screen with a user password prompt shown when the computer is "
"locked"
msgstr ""
"Zaklenjeni zaslon: Zaslon s pozivom za uporabniško geslo, prikazan, ko je "
"računalnik zaklenjen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wallpaper: A desktop background image"
msgstr "Ozadje: slika ozadja namizja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By applying a Global Theme, you can change all of the above together. You "
"can also apply only some components of a Global Theme, such as a color "
"scheme or a window decoration. You can choose which components to change "
"either when applying a Global Theme, or apply individual components by using "
"the other System Settings subsections."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo Globalne Teme lahko spremenite vse zgoraj navedeno skupaj. "
"Uporabite lahko tudi samo nekatere komponente Globalne Teme, na primer "
"barvno shemo ali dekoracijo oken. Izberete lahko, katere komponente želite "
"spremeniti, ko uporabljate Globalno Temo, ali uporabite posamezne komponente "
"z uporabo drugih podrazdelkov sistemskih nastavitev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manage Global Themes"
msgstr "Upravljanje Globalne Teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this module you can:"
msgstr "V tem modulu lahko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "apply Global Themes"
msgstr "uporabite Globalne Teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "install new Global Themes, and remove installed Global Themes"
msgstr "namestite nove Globalne Teme in odstranite nameščene Globalne Teme"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Global Theme manager"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona upravljalnika Globalne Teme"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply Global Themes"
msgstr "Uporabite Globalne Teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can see a preview of each theme by clicking on the image icon that "
"appears when hovering over a theme thumbnail."
msgstr ""
"Predogled vsake teme si lahko ogledate tako, da kliknete ikono slike, ki se "
"prikaže, ko miškin kazalec premaknete nad sličico teme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When clicking on a Global Theme, a dialog will show up asking you which "
"components of the theme you would like to apply. You can select from various "
"appearance settings and the desktop layout."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete Globalne Teme, se prikaže pogovorno okno z vprašanjem, katere "
"komponente teme želite uporabiti. Izbirate lahko med različnimi nastavitvami "
"videza in postavitvijo namizja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:95 index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the Global Theme component chooser"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona izbirnika komponente Globalne Teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After making your selection, click the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button "
"to confirm your choice."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Uporabi</guibutton>, da potrdite svojo "
"izbiro."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Install Global Themes"
msgstr "Namestite Globalne Teme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the button <guilabel>Get New Global Themes...</guilabel>, you can "
"install new Global Themes by third-party providers. You need to be connected "
"to the internet in order to access these themes. Clicking on "
"<guibutton>Install</guibutton> in one of the themes in the dialog will "
"install the chosen Global Theme, and after you close the dialog, your new "
"theme is immediately available."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom <guilabel>Pridobi nove Globalne Teme ...</guilabel> lahko namestite "
"nove lobalne teme tretjih ponudnikov. Za dostop do teh tem morate biti "
"povezani v internet. Če kliknete <guibutton>Namesti</guibutton> v eni od tem "
"v pogovornem oknu, boste namestili izbrano globalno temo in ko zaprete "
"pogovorno okno, bo vaša nova tema takoj na voljo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Get New Global Themes...</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pridobite nove Globalne Teme ...</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Get New Global Themes...</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pridobite nove Globalne Teme ...</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove an installed Global Theme, click on the button with the trash icon "
"that appears when hovering over a theme thumbnail. Note that you can only "
"remove Global Themes that you have downloaded yourself."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti nameščeno globalno temo, kliknite gumb z ikono koša, ki "
"se prikaže, ko premaknete miškin kazalec nad sličico teme. Upoštevajte, da "
"lahko odstranite le globalne teme, ki ste jih prenesli sami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are interested in creating your own theme, you can learn more about "
"the various components <ulink url=\"https://develop.kde.org/docs/plasma/"
"\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če vas zanima ustvarjanje lastne teme, lahko izveste več o različnih "
"komponentah <ulink url=\"https://develop.kde.org/docs/plasma/\">tukaj</"
"ulink>."
